title: Aiptek 3D i2 - side-by-side 3D-test
description:
This is a short clip showing what the Aiptek 3D i2 can do. The video is edited using Magix Movie Edit Pro 17.

The 3D video is in MP4 side-by-side format. Since I haven't got a 3D-TV my self, please leave feeback on how it playback on your 3D-TV set. You can contact me on Twitter @FrankEivind.
